1- Use this to convert Postman collection json to Swagger supported YAML or JSON
    https://www.apimatic.io/dashboard?modal=transform

2- Converts Swagger json to pdf
    https://www.swdoc.org/

3- https://www.npmjs.com/package/swagger-ui-express
    This module allows you to serve auto-generated swagger-ui generated API docs from express, based on a swagger.json file.

4-  yamljs
    To load your swagger specification yaml file you need to use a module able to convert yaml to json; for instance yamljs.

5- https://github.com/expressjs/multer
    Node.js middleware for handling `multipart/form-data`.

6- https://www.npmjs.com/package/@hapi/joi
    The most powerful schema description language and data validator for JavaScript.

7- bcrypt is a password hashing function 
